c Gender Pay Report 2017            Share this page in your favourite social networks.    Print this page      Share on Facebook   Share on Twitter   Add to Pinterest   Share by email   Bookmark or Share          B&Q Plc Gender Pay Report 2017          In line with the new requirement to publish gender pay statistics, B&Q plc published its gender pay report in February 2018. B&Q is committed to being a fair and diverse employer and we welcome the greater transparency on this issue driven by the new gender pay regulations. We are proud of the steps we have taken so far, but we recognise that there is more work to be done. We are focused on enabling all employees, regardless of gender, race, background or any other characteristics, to reach their full potential. We have made great progress in achieving this aim, as illustrated by our gender pay results. Download our 2017 gender pay report here .     Corporate     Sub navigation     Corporate    B&Q; Corporate    About B&Q;    History of B&Q;    Our stores    Our people    Sustainability    Carrier bags    Gender Pay Report 2017                 Back to top     Footer links     Social links    Follow us:                       Business    B&Q; Corporate Homepage    Careers .
